            "options": "<div style='background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fef08a;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:16px;'><h4 style='margin:0 0 8px;color:#854d0e;'>Dynamic Rule Builder</h4><p style='font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;margin:0;line-height:1.5;'>Write conditions using available variables: <code>Revenue_12M</code>, <code>RFM_score</code>, <code>Customer_Age_Days</code>, <code>Total_Orders</code>.<br>Operators: <code>&gt;=</code>, <code>&lt;=</code>, <code>&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;</code>, <code>==</code>, <code>AND</code>, <code>OR</code>.<br>Use <code>DEFAULT</code> for catch-all fallback rule. Engine evaluates top-down by <strong>Priority</strong> (lowest first) until a match is found.</p></div>"
